                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320906-138-off780 t18320906-138-crimeloc782"></join>. On the 22nd of July I missed a spoon, and on the 23rd another from the kitchen cupboard - the prisoner used to come to the house to see a lodger.</p>
